FBIS4-52153 "dreas089_a_94013" FBIS-EAS-94-089 Daily Report 7 May 1994 NORTHEAST ASIA Japan Hata Returns Home From 6-Day Visit to Europe Hata Returns Home From 6-Day Visit to Europe OW0705084894 Tokyo KYODO in English 0827 GMT 7 May 94 OW0705084894 Tokyo KYODO English BFN [Text] Tokyo, May 7 KYODO -- Prime Minister Tsutomu Hata returned home Saturday [7 May] afternoon, ending a six-day official visit to Italy, France, Germany and Belgium. The prime minister held talks with European leaders to establish personal relationships ahead of the July summit in Naples, Italy, of the Group of Seven major industrialized nations, Foreign Ministry officials said.
